\c 4
\s Iminikelo yesono
\p
\v 1 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi isithi:
\v 2 Khuluma ebantwaneni bakoIsrayeli uthi: Uba umphefumulo usona ngokungazi umelana loba yiyiphi imilayo yeN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 5.15,18. Nani 15.22,27. Hez. 18.10; Hlab. 19.12.\x*, engafanele ukwenziwa\x + 4.13,22,27; 5.17. Gen. 34. 7.\x*, wenze okumelene lomunye wayo,
\v 3 uba umpristi ogcotshiweyo esona\x + 8.12; 16.32.\x*, kube licala ebantwini, uzanikela ngesono sakhe asonileyo ijongosi ithole lenkomo elingelasici, eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, libe ngumnikelo wesono.
\v 4 Uzaletha ijongosi emnyango wethente lenhlangano phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 1.3,4.\x*, abeke isandla sakhe enhlokweni yejongosi, alihlabe ijongosi phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 5 Njalo umpristi ogcotshiweyo uzathatha okwegazi lejongosi\x + 4.17. 5.9. 16.14. Nani 19.4. Eks. 29.21. Isa. 52.15.\x*, alilethe ethenteni lenhlangano.
\v 6 Umpristi uzagxamuza-ke umunwe wakhe egazini, afafaze okwegazi kasikhombisa phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 4.17; 5.9. 16.14. Nani 19.4. Eks. 29.21. Isa. 52.15.\x*, phambi kweveyili lendlu engcwele.
\v 7 Njalo umpristi uzafaka okwegazi\x + 8.15; 9.9; 16.18.\x* empondweni zelathi lempepha elephunga elimnandi phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Eks. 39.38.\x*, elisethenteni lenhlangano, athululele lonke igazi lejongosi kungaphansi yelathi lomnikelo wokutshiswa\x + Eks. 29.12; Levi 5.9; 8.15; 9.9.\x*, elisemnyango wethente lenhlangano.
\v 8 Lawo wonke amahwahwa ejongosi lomnikelo wesono uzawasusa kulo, idanga, lawo wonke amahwahwa asemibilini,
\v 9 lezinso zombili lamahwahwa akuzo asezinkalweni, lamahwahwa angaphezu kwesibindi uzawasusa lezinso,
\v 10 njengalokhu kususwa kiyo inkabi yomhlatshelo weminikelo yokuthula\x + 3.3-5.\x*. Umpristi uzakutshisa elathini lomnikelo wokutshiswa.
\v 11 Kodwa isikhumba sejongosi\x + Eks. 29.14. Levi 9.11. Nani 19.5.\x*, lenyama yalo yonke, lenhloko yalo, lemilenze yalo, lemibilini yalo, lomswane walo,
\v 12 yebo, ijongosi lonke uzalikhuphela ngaphandle kwenkamba, alise endaweni ehlambulukileyo, lapho okuthululelwa khona umlotha, alitshise phezu kwenkuni ngomlilo\x + Heb. 13.11.\x*. Lizatshiselwa lapho okuthululelwa khona umlotha.
\p
\v 13 Uba-ke inhlangano yonke yakoIsrayeli isona ngokungazi\x + Nani 15.24.\x*, lendaba ifihlwe emehlweni ebandla\x + 5.2,3,4,17,18.\x*, benze ulutho olumelene loba yiwuphi wemilayo yeN\nd kosi\nd*, okungafanele ukwenziwa, njalo babe lecala,
\v 14 lapho isono abasone bemelene lawo sesisaziwa, ibandla lizanikela ijongosi ithole lenkomo, libe ngumnikelo wesono, lililethe phambi kwethente lenhlangano.
\v 15 Njalo abadala benhlangano bazabeka izandla zabo enhlokweni yejongosi phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 1.4.\x*, lejongosi lizahlatshwa phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 16 Umpristi ogcotshiweyo\x + 4.5-12.\x* uzaletha-ke okwegazi lejongosi ethenteni lenhlangano,
\v 17 lompristi uzagxamuza umunwe wakhe egazini, afafaze kasikhombisa phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*, phambi kweveyili,
\v 18 afake okwegazi empondweni zelathi eliphambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*, elisethenteni lenhlangano, athululele lonke igazi kungaphansi yelathi lomnikelo wokutshiswa, elisemnyango wethente lenhlangano.
\v 19 Uzathatha-ke kilo wonke amahwahwa alo, awatshise elathini.
\v 20 Enze kulo ijongosi, njengakwenze kulo ijongosi lomnikelo wesono, enze njalo kulo\x + 4.3.\x*. Umpristi abenzele inhlawulo yokuthula\x + Nani 15.25,28.\x*, njalo bazathethelelwa.
\v 21 Njalo uzalikhuphela ijongosi ngaphandle kwenkamba, alitshise njengalokho walitshisa ijongosi lokuqala; kungumnikelo wesono webandla.
\p
\v 22 Nxa induna isona, yenza ngokungazi okumelene loba yiwuphi wemilayo yeN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wayo\x + 4.2,13,27.\x*, okungafanele ukwenziwa, njalo ibe lecala,
\v 23 kumbe isono sayo esone imelene lawo sisaziswa kuyo\x + 4.14.\x*, izaletha umnikelo wayo, izinyane lembuzi, iduna elingelasici,
\v 24 ibeke isandla sayo enhlokweni yembuzi\x + 1.4.\x*, iyihlabe endaweni lapho okuhlatshelwa khona umnikelo wokutshiswa phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*; kungumnikelo wesono.
\v 25 Umpristi abesethatha okwegazi lomnikelo wesono ngomunwe wakhe\x + 4.7,18,30,34.\x*, alifake empondweni zelathi lomnikelo wokutshiswa, athululele igazi lawo kungaphansi yelathi lomnikelo wokutshiswa.
\v 26 Lawo wonke amahwahwa awo uzawatshisa elathini njengamahwahwa omhlatshelo weminikelo yokuthula\x + 3.5; 4.10,31.\x*. Ngalokho umpristi uzayenzela inhlawulo yokuthula ngesono sayo\x + 4.20,31,35; 5.10,13,16,18; 6.7.\x*, njalo ithethelelwe.
\p
\v 27 Uba-ke loba ngubani wabantu belizwe esona ngokungazi\x + 4.2; Nani 15.27.\x*, ngoba esenza okumelene loba yiwuphi wemilayo yeN\nd kosi\nd*, okungafanele ukwenziwa, aze abe lecala,
\v 28 kumbe isono sakhe asonileyo sisaziswa kuye\x + 4.14,23.\x*, uzaletha umnikelo wakhe, izinyane lembuzi, isibhuzikazi esingelasici, ngesono sakhe asonileyo.
\v 29 Uzabeka-ke isandla sakhe enhlokweni yomnikelo wesono\x + 4.4,15,24; 1.4.\x*, awuhlabe umnikelo wesono endaweni yomnikelo wokutshiswa.
\v 30 Njalo umpristi uzathatha okwegazi lawo ngomunwe wakhe, alifake empondweni zelathi lomnikelo wokutshiswa, athululele lonke igazi lawo kungaphansi yelathi.
\v 31 Lawo wonke amahwahwa awo uzawasusa\x + 3.14.\x*, njengalokhu amahwahwa esuswa kuwo umhlatshelo weminikelo yokuthula\x + 3.3;4.10,26.\x*, lompristi awatshise elathini abe liphunga elimnandi eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + Gen. 8.21. Eks. 29.18; 1.9,13,17; 2.2,9,12.\x*. Ngalokho umpristi uzamenzela inhlawulo yokuthula, abesethethelelwa\x + 4.20,26,35.\x*.
\v 32 Kodwa uba eletha iwundlu lomnikelo wakhe libe ngumnikelo wesono, uzaletha elisikazi elingelasici\x + 4.28.\x*,
\v 33 abeke isandla sakhe enhlokweni yomnikelo wesono, awuhlabe ube ngumnikelo wesono, endaweni lapho okuhlatshelwa khona umnikelo wokutshiswa.
\v 34 Njalo umpristi uzathatha okwegazi lomnikelo wesono ngomunwe wakhe, alifake empondweni zelathi lomnikelo wokutshiswa, athululele lonke igazi lawo kungaphansi yelathi.
\v 35 Lawo wonke amahwahwa awo uzawasusa njengalokhu amahwahwa ewundlu esuswa kuwo umhlatshelo weminikelo yokuthula\x + 3.9.\x*, lompristi awatshise elathini phezu kweminikelo yeN\nd kosi\nd* eyenziwe ngomlilo. Ngalokho umpristi uzamenzela inhlawulo yokuthula ngesono sakhe asonileyo\x + 4.20,26,31.\x*, njalo uzathethelelwa.